  "title": "Basil-Infused Uruguayan Basil Leaves Bake",
  "description": "A low-sodium-friendly, umami-rich, and moist bake featuring basil leaves in a Uruguayan twist. Perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
