      "amount": "1 tsp",
      "notes": ""
    },
    {
      "name": "Salt-Free Seasoning Blend",
      "amount": "1 tsp",
      "notes": ""
    },
    {
      "name": "Balsamic Vinegar",
      "amount": "2 tbsp",
      "notes": ""
    },
    {
      "name": "Olive Oil",
      "amount": "4 tbsp",
      "notes": ""
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the flour, dried basil, and salt-free seasoning blend.",
    "Add the chopped basil leaves to the dry ingredients and mix well.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the balsamic vinegar and olive oil.",
    "Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and stir until a dough forms.",
    "Transfer the dough to a greased copper-mug and shape into a round mound.",
    "Bake for 35 minutes or until the edges are golden brown.",
    "Remove the bake from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes before slicing."
